title: You're Not The One | Episode 84

description:
Kim Kardashian is suddenly regretting her 'work' comments from earlier in the year, while Jidenna opens up about his polyamorous lifestyle. Plus, why did Chris Rock turn down being the host for the Oscars again next year? Lastly, one man breaks down why a potential love interest is not the one.

The Final Question To Undress got real.  We have an audio clip exchange between a man and a woman- who was wrong?
